module
import v3d
public

: v-box? ( vpt v1 v2 - flag )
    {: vpt v1 v2 :}
    vpt v.x sf@  v1 v.x sf@  f>=   vpt v.x sf@  v2 v.x sf@  f<=  and  not if 0 exit then
    vpt v.y sf@  v1 v.y sf@  f>=   vpt v.y sf@  v2 v.y sf@  f<=  and  not if 0 exit then
    vpt v.z sf@  v1 v.z sf@  f>=   vpt v.z sf@  v2 v.z sf@  f<=  and
;

\ AABB overlap: boxes touch on an axis iff A.min <= B.max AND A.max >= B.min.
\ av1/bv1 are the min corners, av2/bv2 the max corners.
: box-box? ( av1 av2 bv1 bv2 - flag )
    {: av1 av2 bv1 bv2 :}
    av1 v.x sf@  bv2 v.x sf@  f<=  av2 v.x sf@  bv1 v.x sf@  f>=  and  not if 0 exit then
    av1 v.y sf@  bv2 v.y sf@  f<=  av2 v.y sf@  bv1 v.y sf@  f>=  and  not if 0 exit then
    av1 v.z sf@  bv2 v.z sf@  f<=  av2 v.z sf@  bv1 v.z sf@  f>=  and
;

: ball-ball? ( v1 rad1 v2 rad2 - flag )
    {: v1 rad1 v2 rad2 :}
    v1 v2 vdist` rad1 rad2 +` <=
;
